UID:-4cLVArfmO9kyTaZzJG88
SUMMARY:Industrious Coworking Day: Summer Series
DTSTAMP:20260701T033029Z
DTSTART:20260630T083000Z
DESCRIPTION:Register here: https://luma.com/lpkh8qjc \n​Spend the day worki
	ng from Industrious at the ion. \n​Join us for a free coworking day and ex
	perience what a better workday can feel like. Bring your laptop\, settle i
	n\, enjoy coffee and refreshments\, and get your work done in a space desi
	gned for focus\, comfort\, and connection. \n​Whether you’re working solo\
	, meeting a colleague\, or looking for a new home base for your team\, thi
	s is an easy way to experience Industrious firsthand. \n​During the day\, 
	you’ll have access to: \n​• Thoughtfully designed shared workspace • Coffe
	e\, breakfast\, and snacks • Comfortable common areas • On-site support fr
	om our local team • Opportunities to connect with other professionals in t
	he space \n​As well as our Grant Writing Workshop! \n​Industrious offers c
	oworking\, private offices\, suites\, meeting rooms\, and flexible workpla
	ce options for individuals and teams. With 250+ locations across 80+ citie
	s globally\, we make it easier to find a workspace that works for you. Spa
	ce is limited. RSVP to reserve your spot. \n​Parking:\nParking is free for
	 the first 3 hours\, then $10 for the remainder of the day. \n​We look for
	ward to welcoming you!\n\nhttps://iondistrict.com/event/industrious-cowork
	ing-day-summer-series/\n\nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/industrious-coworking-day-summer-series/
LOCATION:Industrious\, 4201 Main St\, Houston\, TX\, 77002
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ion-district
CATEGORIES:Ion District
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT9H
END:VEVENT
