SUMMARY:Unwind & Win at the Hyatt!
DTSTAMP:20260701T033029Z
DTSTART:20260702T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:Looking for the perfect spot to transition from the workday to 
	the weekend? Join the Energy Corridor community for a sophisticated happy 
	hour at the Hyatt Regency Houston West. Experience the elegant atmosphere 
	of Black Gold Bar\; it’s the perfect opportunity to connect with District 
	leaders and professionals in a relaxed\, beautiful setting. \nBeyond the g
	reat drinks and atmosphere\, they’re bringing the community together with 
	some exciting weekly perks: \n\nWeekly Prize Drawings: Every Thursday at 6
	:45 PM.\nMonthly Grand Prize: A lucky winner receives a 1-night weekend st
	ay!\nVendor Showcase Corner: Discover and support local District businesse
	s.\n\n  \nCome for the drinks\, stay for the connections! \nWhen: Thursday
	s – 4:00 PM – 7:00 PM \nLocation: Black Gold Bar | 13210 Katy Fwy\, Housto
	n\, TX 77079 \nDownload the Happy Hour Menu\n\nhttps://energycorridor.org/
	event/unwind-and-win-at-the-hyatt/2026-07-02/\n\nFrom Energy Corridor Farm
	ers Market
URL:https://energycorridor.org/event/unwind-and-win-at-the-hyatt/2026-07-02
	/
