UID:DpWWbRNKhIrpI_y2YZOhK
SUMMARY:Retro Video Game Expo III
DTSTAMP:20260701T033030Z
DTSTART:20260815T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:🕹️ Houston\, Press Start on a Weekend of Pure Retro Nostalgia! 👾
	 \nStep back into the golden era of gaming at Retro Video Game Expo III\, 
	a two-day celebration of classic consoles\, arcade legends\, competitive r
	etro tournaments\, and nonstop free play. From expanded free-play zones sp
	anning the 80s and beyond to live\, high-energy tournament matchups and a 
	collector-focused marketplace\, this expo is built for gamers who chase hi
	gh scores and grail finds. \n  \n🗓️ Date & Time: August 15–16\, 2026 | 10AM
	–5PM \n📍 Location: 9700 Bissonnet St #1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n💥 FREE E
	NTRY. FREE PARKING. FREE PLAY. \n\n🎮 Event Highlights\n🎮 Retro Video Game 
	Marketplace – All Weekend \nStep into a collector’s paradise. Vendors from
	 across the region are bringing vintage consoles\, original cartridges\, i
	mports\, manuals\, accessories\, and hard-to-find titles. This is where tr
	easures respawn. \n🚨 Want to vend? Sign up here 👉 https://tinyurl.com/Hous
	tonVendors \n  \n🎮 Free-Play Zone – ALL Day \nJump on 80’s Arcades & Class
	ic Consoles and relive the games that made gaming legendary. More setups a
	nd activities to be announced soon! \n\n🤝 Calling All Collaborators & Retr
	o Communities\nThis event is built with the community for community! We’re
	 actively looking to partner with: \n🏁 Tournament organizers → https://for
	ms.gle/74Qvuv9PFzeDVF1V8 \n🕹️ Pinball/Arcade Hosts → https://forms.gle/74Qv
	uv9PFzeDVF1V8 \n🎤 Workshops & Panels → https://forms.gle/q2nCKsZ6FEVZBgqW9
	 \n🙌 Volunteer Sign-Up → https://forms.gle/15zMGTqZPSGKjGdy6 \n🎮 Vendor Ap
	plications → https://tinyurl.com/CCSGuestVendorFromHouston \nIf you’ve eve
	r wanted to be part of event\, bring your passion! Let’s chat! 📩 \n  \n🏨 S
	pecial Hotel Deals \nEnjoy a special rate of $79/night — 2 Queens at Towne
	Place Suites\, only 15 minutes distance from the action! \nBook your stay 
	👉🏻 https://www.marriott.com/event-reservations/reservation-link.mi?id=17678
	23967549&key=CORP&app=resvlink \n  \nBring your crew\, grab a controller\,
	 and let’s relive the golden age of gaming together. 👾✨\n\nhttps://ccs-hou
	ston.com/events/retro-video-game-expo-iii/\n\nFrom CCS Houston
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/retro-video-game-expo-iii/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ccs-houston
CATEGORIES:CCS Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT31H
END:VEVENT
